# Project Structure

## Root Directory

```
.
├── app/                 # Core application code (Remix)
├── public/              # Static assets served by the web server
├── drizzle/             # Drizzle ORM configuration and migrations
├── vite.config.ts       # Vite configuration
├── biome.json           # Biome formatter/linter configuration
├── tailwind.config.ts   # Tailwind CSS configuration
├── remotion.config.ts   # Remotion configuration
├── .npmrc               # NPM configuration (likely for PNPM)
├── postcss.config.js    # PostCSS configuration
├── components.json      # UI component configuration (e.g., Shadcn UI)
├── .node-version        # Specifies Node.js version
```

## `app/` Directory

```
app/
├── types.ts             # TypeScript type definitions
├── schema.ts            # Schema definitions (likely Zod or similar)
├── routes/              # Remix routes
├── remotion/            # Remotion video components/compositions
├── utils/               # Utility functions
├── constants.ts         # Application constants
├── components/          # Reusable UI components (likely Shadcn UI)
├── tailwind.css         # Main Tailwind CSS file
├── lib/                 # Library code (e.g., third-party integrations, core logic)
├── db/                  # Database related code (e.g., Drizzle schema, queries)
├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks
├── api/                 # API specific logic (potentially serverless functions or actions)
├── entry.server.tsx     # Remix server entry point
├── root.tsx             # Remix root layout/component
├── config.ts            # Application configuration
├── entry.client.tsx     # Remix client entry point
```
